trans-unit.source: A factory class for creating <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.ActiveDirectoryRole"></xref> objects from Windows NT aliases, e-mail addresses, and security identifiers (SIDs).
trans-unit.target: En fabrikken klasse for oppretting av <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.ActiveDirectoryRole"> </xref> objekter fra Windows NT-aliaser, e-postadresser og sikkerhetsidentifikatorer (SID).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] All methods in ActiveDirectoryRoleFactory are static and no instance needs to be created.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Alle metodene i ActiveDirectoryRoleFactory er statisk, og ingen forekomst må opprettes.

trans-unit.source: The constructor is hidden.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren er skjult.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Configuration.ActiveDirectoryRoleFactoryConfiguration"></xref> object that is associated with the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.ActiveDirectoryRoleFactory"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Configuration.ActiveDirectoryRoleFactoryConfiguration"> </xref> objekt som er knyttet til den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.ActiveDirectoryRoleFactory"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Configuration.ActiveDirectoryRoleFactoryConfiguration> object is used for changing the standard Active Directory schema properties that the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ActiveDirectoryRole> class uses.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Configuration.ActiveDirectoryRoleFactoryConfiguration>objektet brukes til å endre standardegenskapene for Active Directory-skjemaet som den <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ActiveDirectoryRole>klasse bruker.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ActiveDirectoryRole> </xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Configuration.ActiveDirectoryRoleFactoryConfiguration>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Configuration.ActiveDirectoryRoleFactoryConfiguration"></xref> object associated with the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.ActiveDirectoryRoleFactory"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Configuration.ActiveDirectoryRoleFactoryConfiguration"> </xref> tilknyttet den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.ActiveDirectoryRoleFactory"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Creates an instance of <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.ActiveDirectoryRole"></xref> using the specified Windows NT alias.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en forekomst av <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.ActiveDirectoryRole"> </xref> ved hjelp av det angitte Windows NT-aliaset.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ActiveDirectoryRole> is a concrete implementation of the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowRole> abstract class that is used to access Active Directory functionality.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ActiveDirectoryRole>er en konkret implementering av den <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowRole>abstrakt klasse som brukes til å få tilgang til Active Directory-funksjonen.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowRole></xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ActiveDirectoryRole>

trans-unit.source: Typically, the Active Directory store is used for storing organizational information for personnel.
trans-unit.target: Active Directory-butikken brukes vanligvis til å lagre informasjon om organisasjonen for støttepersonell.

trans-unit.source: The main purpose for the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ActiveDirectoryRole> is for making queries against such organizational information for business reasons.
trans-unit.target: Det primære formålet for den <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ActiveDirectoryRole>er for å foreta spørringer mot organisasjonens informasjon business grunner.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ActiveDirectoryRole>
